{
  "stem": "10768.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there was all kinds of dietary treatment, which in Europe-- at that time in Poland, we didn't hear about it before the war.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Anyhow, I was there until beginning of 1944-- the end of 1943.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Beginning of 1944, I was inducted into the Polish army.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was not reading at that time, newspapers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I heard about it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the clinic was a Jewish girl whose parents ran away from Rostov.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In Rostov, every Russian-- Kharkov, Rostov-- Jews, Jews liked to concentrate in city.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So she had already, at that time, some news that Jews were being killed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But from whatever happened in Poland, I had no idea.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when I came on to Polish territory, then I knew already.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But this was in Chardjou, which was pretty deep.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was near, near Iran.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't read, read-- even the Russian papers were not specifically mentioning that so many, so many Jews were killed.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were saying-- when the Germans were coming forward-- they were saying in our town, we abandoned this and this town.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in this town, the Germans came in, and they killed so and so many Russian--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Citizens.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Thank you for helping me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they did not specify Jews-- not until I came on to Polish territory.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "From there, again, they put us on a train.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I say us because when I came on the train, I met quite a few men who were also sending-- sent from all kind of parts of Russia to go.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't know exactly where.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we befriended ourselves on the train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it took, again, two weeks or more.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were only traveling at night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "During the day, we were still afraid for bombing or for planes, the German trains-- planes.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
